It also calls for more effective monitoring of the ways in which the Funds are used and for a more focused strategy with regard to industrial restructuring and its social impact.
It confirms support for regions that have suffered as a result of the âstatistical effectâ, it has adopted amendments that we tabled to eliminate the expression âtemporary phasing-outâ and to provide phasing-out support for current Objective 1 regions; it calls for the special status of the outermost regions to be preserved and for specific programmes to be kept on, even if they are no longer in Objective 1 regions.
